{"tid":1696559,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iOS 13.3 Beta1必升！減少App reload + Emoji Keyboard可關閉Memoji","createTime":"2019-11-06T08:43:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T09:12:07.000Z","uid":109923,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"9560578bf518df976c566e79b3465aec5b55806b","tid":1696559,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:43:05.000Z","msg":"不少升級了 iOS 13.2 的用戶表示 iOS 13.2 比以往 iOS 12 在清理背景程式(Kill App)方面顯得更為頻密，對用戶造成不便。<br />\n<br />\n有用戶指當在使用一些較需記憶體的應用時，例如轉換到 iMessage 或 Camera App，再回到原本的應用就會發現原本的 App 已被 Kill，需要重新載入。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/arQJtg1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FarQJtg1.png&h=fea7d632&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這情況也開始被 App Developer 察覺，例如有 SSH 遠端連線 App 開發者表示，當用戶切換到其他 App 時，原本的 SSH 連線竟被中斷。也有開發者表示，iPhone 11 的 Camera 功能需要很多資源，每次切換到 Camera App 後再回到先前開啟的 App 就會被發現舊 App 已被 Kill。<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">似乎 iPhone 11/11 Pro 會較易出現這情況，因為新 iPhone 的deep fusion攝影功能比以往需要更多記憶體。</span></span></strong>而這是 Bugs 或是硬件的限制，但顯然開發者對 iOS 13 的記憶體控制抱有不滿。"},{"pid":"bc9a55d0ce94cc42fbd45e5d40e377283ee7b3ed","tid":1696559,"uid":52623,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:38:49.000Z","msg":"似乎冇乜伏 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9077663340b84366a17b65a53943a62930365137","tid":1696559,"uid":1130,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:41:36.000Z","msg":"13.2嘅舊iPhone一樣秒kill<br />\n升完暫時ok<br />\n不過safari都有reload"},{"pid":"1902db494bd00c315b5ec32bd3b743bda30ce5ba","tid":1696559,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9077663340b84366a17b65a53943a62930365137","tid":1696559,"uid":1130,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:41:36.000Z","msg":"13.2嘅舊iPhone一樣秒kill<br />\n升完暫時ok<br />\n不過safari都有reload"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:58:37.000Z","msg":"